@ChatbotService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5008

# Health check
GET {{ChatbotService_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

# Readiness check
GET {{ChatbotService_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

###

# Send chat message
POST {{ChatbotService_HostAddress}}/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello, how can I reset my password?",
  "sessionId": "test-session-001",
  "context": {
    "userId": "user-123",
    "clientType": "web"
  }
}

###

# Get chat history
GET {{ChatbotService_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/test-session-001/history?limit=10
Accept: application/json

